data.description: Are you in search of an enchanting Colonial-style residence, perhaps in the picturesque Boro of High Bridge, New Jersey? Look no further; we've got you covered. This property boasts three bedrooms, a well-appointed bathroom, a generously sized living room, and an inviting eat-in kitchen featuring elegant granite countertops and a central island. This home is sure to meet all your criteria. Don't hesitate, schedule a viewing today to fully immerse yourself in the delights of living in the charming High Bridge Boro.
